Package: stannis
Type: Package
Title: Handles output from Stan (mc-stan.org)
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-01-07
Author: Krzysztof Sakrejda
Maintainer: Krzysztof Sakrejda <k@fawkes.io>
Description: Work with CmdStan from R, using standard R tools. Run models specified in .yaml files, store output in standard hierarchy, post-process output to create data frame or arrays, merge chains, pick out specific parameters from larger model outputs.  Planned: faster .csv reader, run diagnostics directly. 
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    yaml
Suggests:
    rappdirs
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
